{"id": 57666, "date": "2025-07-11T04:00:38", "date_gmt": "2025-07-11T11:00:38", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57666"}, "modified": "2026-03-12T10:18:34", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-12T17:18:34", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-july-11-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/11/kingdom-of-days-july-11-2/", "title": {"rendered": "July 11"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1971:\u00a0</strong>The Bruce Springsteen Band opens for Humble Pie at Asbury Park&#8217;s Sunshine In. Peter Frampton is impressed enough by Bruce and the band to offer them a gig opening for Humble Pie around the country, as well as an introduction to their record label. Mystifyingly, Tinker West (Bruce&#8217;s manager at the time) declines the offers.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"11214\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1971-07-11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1971-07-11.jpg?fit=500%2C394&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"500,394\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1971-07-11\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1971-07-11.jpg?fit=300%2C236&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1971-07-11.jpg?fit=500%2C394&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-11214 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1971-07-11.jpg?resize=500%2C394&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1971-07-11.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1971-07-11.jpg?resize=300%2C236&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19474\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1971-07-11-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1971-07-11.jpg?fit=672%2C959&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"672,959\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1593174483&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1971-07-11\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1971-07-11.jpg?fit=210%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1971-07-11.jpg?fit=672%2C959&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19474 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1971-07-11.jpg?resize=672%2C959&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"672\" height=\"959\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1971-07-11.jpg?w=672&amp;ssl=1 672w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1971-07-11.jpg?resize=210%2C300&amp;ssl=1 210w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 672px) 100vw, 672px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>Bruce records overdubs for &#8220;Kitty&#8217;s Back&#8221; and &#8220;Evacuation of the West&#8221; at 914 Sound Studios in Blauvelt, New York.</p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band work on &#8220;Badlands&#8221; at Atlantic Studio in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>1979:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band work on &#8220;I Wanna Marry You&#8221; during a recording session at the Power Station in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>Clarence Clemons opens his new nightclub, Big Man&#8217;s West, in Red Bank. Bruce makes an appearance with Clarence and his band to mark the occasion, playing six songs, including a set-closing &#8220;You Can&#8217;t Sit Down&#8221; and &#8220;Cadillac Ranch.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-MByTu4nD-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/MByTu4nD?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"68248\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/11/kingdom-of-days-july-11-2/1981-07-11-rotated/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/1981-07-11-rotated-1.jpg?fit=549%2C984&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"549,984\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1981-07-11-rotated\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/1981-07-11-rotated-1.jpg?fit=167%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/1981-07-11-rotated-1.jpg?fit=549%2C984&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-68248\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/1981-07-11-rotated-1.jpg?resize=549%2C984&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"984\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/1981-07-11-rotated-1.jpg?w=549&amp;ssl=1 549w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/1981-07-11-rotated-1.jpg?resize=167%2C300&amp;ssl=1 167w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 549px) 100vw, 549px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2002:\u00a0</strong>Bruce kicks off rehearsals for the Rising Tour with the E Street Band at the Expo Theater in Fort Monmouth, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"11215\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2002-07-11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2002-07-11.jpg?fit=426%2C287&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"426,287\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2002-07-11\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2002-07-11.jpg?fit=300%2C202&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2002-07-11.jpg?fit=426%2C287&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-11215 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2002-07-11.jpg?resize=426%2C287&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"426\" height=\"287\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2002-07-11.jpg?w=426&amp;ssl=1 426w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2002-07-11.jpg?resize=300%2C202&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 426px) 100vw, 426px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2008:\u00a0</strong>It&#8217;s Christmas in July when Bruce honors one last sign request when the Magic Tour stops in Helsinki: &#8220;Santa Claus is Comin&#8217; to Town&#8221; is the second to last song of the night.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0stcLuNJlIQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2009:\u00a0</strong>Jake Clemons makes his debut on an E Street Band stage when he guest-stars on sax during &#8220;Tenth Avenue Freeze-Out&#8221; as the Working on a Dream Tour stops for the first of two nights at RDS Arena in Dublin. (How strange to see him next to Clarence&#8211;the intersection of E Street Past and Present!) Bruce&#8217;s son Evan joins the band as well, playing acoustic guitar on &#8220;American Land.&#8221; Tour debuting tonight: &#8220;You Can Look (But You Better Not Touch).&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/BLQMbiz0mYE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/_mlMGhN5lkQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xxhkJeqnbIE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xcdkrSAr_sQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/mxXPSPYziAA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kfVHI3RGLVI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2012:\u00a0</strong>Bruce opens with an acoustic &#8220;The Ghost of Tom Joad&#8221; at his second show ever in Prague, and his first with the E Street Band. The tour premiere of &#8220;This Hard Land&#8221; is a set list highlight.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ywd8HRiIDCQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/1cJTdhdiXiw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2013:\u00a0</strong>A stunning night in Rome on the Wrecking Ball Tour: the set list is full of gems but the gleaming highlight is the unexpected complete second album side of the <em>Wild &amp; Innocent</em> album, including a full string section on &#8220;New York City Serenade.&#8221; Watch that pro-shot clip below. This show is also available as part of the official archive series.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/T-IZWISZ8CY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/2-ap3TvDWXk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SxVeIcOx8Nc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/oLvxQ10RMHQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/aI8k7Njkaww?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2016:\u00a0</strong>A wild night in Paris for the first of two shows on the River Tour (2016 Edition). Bruce opens with a solo piano &#8220;Incident on 57th Street&#8221; followed by the tour premiere of &#8220;Reason to Believe.&#8221; &#8220;Into the Fire&#8221; and &#8220;Nebraska&#8221; receive tour premieres as well. Elliott and Gaspard Murphy make a customary guest appearance during the encores, but during &#8220;Ramrod,&#8221; the power goes out and Bruce finishes the song mic-less before taking a break until the power is restored.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7_MB4ABloko?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/k9JN66DWcF4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/J7nCcRa0UhY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0sj9frOE6oQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HjxRYm8gvjo?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2018:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>continues its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>2023:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band take the stage at Parken Stadium in Copenhagen, their first of two shows in Denmark.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cqXj_l793u0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-ori